getCoins:
query GetCoins($activeSection: SectionInput!, $pagination: PaginationInput, $order: OrderInput) {
        coins(section: $activeSection, pagination: $pagination, order: $order) {
          id
          name
          chain
          symbol
          launchDate
          totalUpvotes
          upvotesToday
          isUpvoted
 logo
          createdOn
          isCaptchaEnabled
          isLogoDownloaded
          useManualPrice
          currentMarketCap
          oneHourComparison
          oneDayComparison
          version
          isVerified
          isHoneypot
          isScanned
          audit
          __typename
        }
      }
